mintinstall (7.9.6) tessa; urgency=medium

  [ Clement Lefebvre ]
  * Fix export_flatpak

  [ Michael Webster ]
  * mintinstall: Add a refresh menu item, and distinguish an (incorrectly) empty category from an empty search result so we can provide a more helpful message and allow the user to refresh if necessary.
  * housekeeping: cast PosixPath to string for python3 < 3.6
  * mintinstall: terminate() the review and housekeeping processes when closing the program, they won't terminate properly when the parent process is killed.
  * _apt.py: Add "libk3b7" to filter exceptions.
  * cache.py: Check that the system cache can be read before using.
  * all: Don't require flatpak to be installed. (#218)

  [ gm10 ]
  * _apt.py: whitelist libimage-exiftool-perl (#217)

