 -- Clement Lefebvre <root@linuxmint.com>  Wed, 22 Nov 2017 17:32:46 +0000

mintinstall (7.8.6) sylvia; urgency=medium

  [ Clement Lefebvre ]
  * Categories: Sorted/Reviewed some of the lists
